<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然然<colour id="65535" />带来的<delay8 />花朵种子和灌木树苗<delay20 />
大多都是在<colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />里买不到的哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且质量也很好，<delay20 />我每次去那家伙的店里，
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都忍不住要买上许多！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不同种类的灌木，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
花期也都各不相同。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />根据季节来选择种植的灌木种类，<delay20 />
也是很有趣的事哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次种哪种好呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到花草树木时，<delay20 />
总会让人觉得<delay8 />很安心呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以这地球日为契机，<delay20 />
能够添置一些喜欢的植物，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得很开心！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />流·<delay8 />园艺技巧，
你想学习吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这技巧就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />凭气势和直觉，<delay8 />尽情种植自己喜欢的花草！<delay frames="30" />
这就是我的独门秘诀<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />完全没有参考价值吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想为<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="32" />上的环境做些贡献，<delay8 />
于是就决定去除草，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />那家伙看到后<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然<delay20 />对我说，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“难道<delay20 />你是杂草之神派来的使者吗？”<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那家伙<delay20 />有时候还真是不可思议<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
